  if (lowerCaseCountry) {
    // Convert the cities keys to lowercase and check if the country exists
    return (
      lowerCaseCountry in
      Object.keys(cities).reduce((obj, key) => {
        obj[key.toLowerCase()] = cities[key];
        return obj;
      }, {})
    );
  }
  if (lowerCaseCityName) {
    for (const country in cities) {
      if (
        cities[country].some((city) => city.toLowerCase() === lowerCaseCityName)
      ) {
        return true;
      }
    }
  }

  return false;
